### Problem24


Fill in the blanks in the following TOY program that reads two inputs from Stdin, multiplies them using repeated addition, and prints the result to StdOut.

10: 8 A F F  
reads from StdIn to R[A]  
11: 8 B F F  
reads from StdIn to R[B]  

12: 7 C O O  
R[C] <- 0000  

13: 7 1 0 1   
R[1] <- 0001  

14: C A _____(0)\___ _____(1)\___  
HINT: if R[A] == 0, we have our answer!  

15: 1 C _____(2)\___ _____(3)\___  
HINT: add something to R[C]  

16: 2 A _____(4)\___ _____(5)\___  
HINT: subtract something from R[A]

17: _____(6)\___ _____(7)\___ _____(8)\___ _____(9)\___   
HINT: we're not done yet!

18: 9 C F F  
print R[C] to StdOut

19: 0 0 0 0   
halt
